This bot is to refresh and retrive GNIB / IRP appointment and push notification to my private chime room.

Main logic is referred from [harshp](https://harshp.com/dev/utils/gnib-appointments/).

Developed with shell script and running on my VPS.

--------------------

Ref:
[‘Bots’ used to block immigrants in Ireland from making visa appointments](https://www.irishtimes.com/news/social-affairs/bots-used-to-block-immigrants-in-ireland-from-making-visa-appointments-1.3620957)



